      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm doing a paper for my psych history class on the eugenics movement from the early 1900s. can u help me out by breaking down the actual arguments they used to justify racial hierarchies? like, what was their 'scientific' reasoning for why certain races were seen as superior or inferior? i just need the main points they used back then for my notes.",
